---
title: "{{ title }}"
date: {{ date_iso }}
draft: false
tags:
{%- for topic in topics %}
  - {{ topic | replace('"', "'") | tojson }}
{%- endfor %}
levels:
{%- for level in active_levels %}
  - {{ level }}
{%- endfor %}
video_url: "{{ video_url }}"
audio_url: "{{ audio_url }}"
summary: "{{ topics[:3] | join('、') }}"
---

{% raw %}{{< media-player >}}{% endraw %}

<script type="application/json" id="segments-data">
{{ segments | tojson }}
</script>

<div class="cefr-tabs">
  <button class="cefr-tab active" data-level="summary">📋 摘要</button>
  <button class="cefr-tab" data-level="transcript">📝 逐字稿</button>
{%- for level in active_levels %}
  <button class="cefr-tab" data-level="{{ level }}">{% if level == "A1" %}🟢 A1{% elif level == "A2" %}🟡 A2{% elif level == "B1" %}🔴 B1{% endif %}</button>
{%- endfor %}
</div>

<div class="cefr-content active" data-level="summary">

{% if summary_zh %}
{{ summary_zh }}
{% endif %}

{% if active_levels %}
<p class="cefr-hint">📊 本集學習內容：{%- for level in active_levels %}{% if level == "A1" %} 🟢 A1{% elif level == "A2" %} 🟡 A2{% elif level == "B1" %} 🔴 B1{% endif %}（{{ levels[level].vocabulary | length }} 單字 · {{ levels[level].grammar | length }} 文法 · {{ levels[level].patterns | length }} 句型）{%- endfor %} — 點擊上方分頁查看</p>
{% endif %}

</div>

<div class="cefr-content" data-level="transcript">

<div class="transcript-table">

| 時間 | Deutsch | 中文翻譯 |
|:-----|:--------|:---------|
{%- for seg in segments %}
| <span class="ts-link" data-time="{{ seg.start }}">{{ seg.start }}</span> | {{ seg.de | replace("|", "｜") }} | {{ seg.zh | replace("|", "｜") }} |
{%- endfor %}

</div>

</div>

{% if levels.get("A1") and (levels.A1.vocabulary or levels.A1.grammar or levels.A1.patterns) %}
<div class="cefr-content" data-level="A1">

### 🟢 A1 — 初學者區 Anfänger

{% if levels.A1.vocabulary %}
#### 📖 單字 Wortschatz

| 單字 | 詞性 | 中文 | 例句 | 翻譯 | 🔊 |
|:-----|:-----|:-----|:-----|:-----|:---:|
{%- for v in levels.A1.vocabulary %}
| **{{ v.word }}** | {{ v.article or "" }} | {{ v.meaning }} | {{ v.example | replace("|", "｜") }} | {{ v.example_zh | replace("|", "｜") }} | {% if v.time %}<span class="ts-link" data-time="{{ v.time }}">{{ v.time }}</span>{% endif %} |
{%- endfor %}

{% endif %}
{% if levels.A1.grammar %}
#### 📝 文法 Grammatik

{% for g in levels.A1.grammar %}
<details>
<summary><strong>{{ g.rule }}</strong>{% if g.time %} <span class="ts-link" data-time="{{ g.time }}">🔊 {{ g.time }}</span>{% endif %}</summary>

> **德文**：{{ g.german }}
>
> **中文**：{{ g.chinese }}

{{ g.explanation }}

</details>

{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
{% if levels.A1.patterns %}
#### 💬 句型 Satzmuster

{% for p in levels.A1.patterns %}
- **{{ p.pattern }}**{% if p.time %} <span class="ts-link" data-time="{{ p.time }}">🔊 {{ p.time }}</span>{% endif %}

  - 🇩🇪 {{ p.example }}
  - 🇹🇼 {{ p.translation }}
  - 💡 {{ p.note }}

{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

</div>
{% endif %}

{% if levels.get("A2") and (levels.A2.vocabulary or levels.A2.grammar or levels.A2.patterns) %}
